execute

public void execute(JHOVE2 jhove2,
                    Source source,
                    Input input)
             throws JHOVE2Exception
If Source is an aggregate source, invokes aggregate identifier to detect possible ClumpSource instances in the aggregate; If any ClumpSources are found, performs call back to JHOVE2 framework to characterize them

Parameters:
jhove2 - JHOVE2 framework object
source - Source unit
input - Source input, which for an aggregate source will be null
Throws:
JHOVE2Exception
